---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Housing Assistance | Veteran Support Services"
  description="Learn about housing assistance available to UK veterans through the Armed Forces Compensation Scheme. Discover support for finding accommodation, adapting homes, and housing-related financial aid.">
  <div class="container my-5">
    <h1 class="display-4 mb-4">Housing Assistance for Veterans</h1>
    <div class="row g-4">
      <div class="col-lg-8">
        <p class="lead">The Armed Forces Compensation Scheme (AFCS) recognises the importance of stable housing for veterans. This page outlines the various forms of housing assistance available to help veterans secure suitable accommodation and adapt their homes as needed.</p>
        
        <h2 class="h3 mt-4">Finding Accommodation</h2>
        <p>Support services to help veterans find suitable housing include:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Priority status on social housing waiting lists</li>
          <li>Assistance with private rental applications</li>
          <li>Access to veteran-specific housing schemes</li>
          <li>Temporary accommodation for those at risk of homelessness</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="h3 mt-4">Home Adaptations</h2>
        <p>For veterans with disabilities, we offer support for home adaptations:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Assessment of adaptation needs</li>
          <li>Funding for necessary modifications</li>
          <li>Installation of mobility aids and equipment</li>
          <li>Advice on creating accessible living spaces</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="h3 mt-4">Financial Assistance</h2>
        <p>Various forms of financial aid are available for housing-related expenses:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Grants for deposits and first month's rent</li>
          <li>Support with mortgage payments in cases of injury-related financial hardship</li>
          <li>Assistance with utility bills and council tax</li>
          <li>Budgeting advice for housing costs</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="h3 mt-4">Supported Housing</h2>
        <p>For veterans requiring additional support:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Access to supported housing schemes</li>
          <li>Sheltered accommodation options</li>
          <li>Residential care facilities for those with complex needs</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="h3 mt-4">Homelessness Prevention</h2>
        <p>Services aimed at preventing and addressing homelessness among veterans:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Early intervention programmes</li>
          <li>Emergency accommodation services</li>
          <li>Support for rough sleepers</li>
          <li>Assistance with tenancy sustainment</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="h3 mt-4">Housing Advice and Advocacy</h2>
        <p>Expert guidance to help navigate housing challenges:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>One-to-one housing advice sessions</li>
          <li>Assistance with housing benefit applications</li>
          <li>Advocacy in dealings with landlords or housing authorities</li>
          <li>Legal advice on housing rights</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-4">
        <div class="card bg-light mb-4">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h3 class="h5">Related Services</h3>
            <ul class="list-unstyled">
              <li><a href="/support/financial-advice" class="text-decoration-none">Financial Advice</a></li>
              <li><a href="/medical/long-term-care" class="text-decoration-none">Long-term Care Options</a></li>
              <li><a href="/support/mental-health" class="text-decoration-none">Mental Health Support</a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card mb-4">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h3 class="h5">Housing Support Helpline</h3>
            <p>For urgent housing advice or to discuss your accommodation needs, contact our helpline.</p>
            <p class="fw-bold">0800 XXX XXXX</p>
            <a href="/housing-support" class="btn btn-primary">Learn More</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
